<div class="landing-section">
	<h3 class="heading-text">Built For The Modern Climber</h3>
	<p class="body-text-x">Figure Eight organizes trips to the best climbing locations in the world. Guided by 24/7 staff, our trips provide technical expertise, beautiful lodging, and hearty meals, so you and your friends can focus on adventure. Five percent of all our proceeds go to climbing foundations such as <a href="#">The Access Fund</a> and <a href="#">Friends of Muir Valley</a>.</p>
