		<div class="benefit-paragraph">
			<p>Our cabins offer comfortable beds, beautiful views, and pristine bathroom amenities so you can relax at the end of the day. We stock the kitchen for breakfast and lunch and explore local hotspots together for dinner.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="product-benefit benefit-padded benefit-groups">
		<div class="benefit-title">Dynamic Groups</div>
		<div class="benefit-paragraph">
			<p>Whether you join solo or book with a group, you'll be climbing with a tight-knit cohort of 8-12 people who share a passion for climbing and having a good time. </p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="product-benefit benefit-support">
		<div class="benefit-title">24/7 Support</div>
		<div class="benefit-paragraph">
			<p>Unlike traditional climbing guides who leave you at sundown, our knowledgable and friendly staff supports the group all day and night with plan changes, local recs, and troubleshooting.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="product-benefit benefit-padded benefit-skills">
		<div class="benefit-title">Skills-Building</div>
		<div class="benefit-paragraph">
			<p>We believe learning and climbing go hand-in-hand. Build your knowledge of anchor-building, sport leading, or trad protection in a safe environment. Our trips are best-suited for climbers who can lead at least 5.9 indoors, but beginners are welcome, too!</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="product-benefit benefit-fun">
		<div class="benefit-title">Fun Extras</div>
		<div class="benefit-paragraph">
			<p>Each trip is accompanied by a guy with a camera, so you'll come away with some cool shots (yup, we took all the ones on this website). We like playing with drones, too.</p>
		</div>
